        en:
          '<p><span style="color: rgb(77,81,86);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: arial, sans-serif;">Human resources is the set of the people who make up the workforce of an organization, business sector, industry, or economy. A narrower concept is human capital, the knowledge which the individuals embody. Similar terms include manpower, labour, personnel, associates or simply people.</span></p>\n',
        'zh-hk':
          '<p><span style="color: rgb(77,81,86);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 14px;font-family: arial, sans-serif;">人力資源，是指一個機構中由人所組成的勞動力。人力資源的安排、運用稱為「人力資源管理」，關鍵功能是『在合適的時間，將合適的人員，安排在合適的職務上』，乃企業用來治理與運用人力資本的部門。往昔人力資源管理泛稱為「勞動力管理」和「人事管理」，曾經僅專注於「工資計算和發放」和「雇員檔案管理」的功能。</span></p>\n',
